          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1670336413043-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1670336413043-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1670336413043-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop the <strong>smoked</strong> <strong>basa fillets</strong> into large, bite-sized pieces</p><p>Once reduced, top the<strong> </strong>sauce with the <strong>chopped basa</strong> and cook, covered, for 2-3 min further or until the fish is cooked through</p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
